    <div class="container">
        <h1>Privacy Policy - Jaylon Dental Cleaning Booking (Educational Demo)</h1>

        <div class="note">
            <strong>Note:</strong> This app is developed solely for educational or capstone project purposes. It is not intended for commercial use or real dental bookings. Any data entered is for demonstration only.
        </div>

        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>For demonstration purposes, we may collect minimal information such as:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Name and Email:</strong> Provided for booking simulation.</li>
            <li><strong>Messenger ID:</strong> To demonstrate bot interaction.</li>
            <li><strong>Booking Details:</strong> Appointment date, time, or service preferences for demo purposes only.</li>
            <li><strong>Technical Data:</strong> Device type, operating system, and browser info for testing and analytics.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use this data only to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Demonstrate the app’s booking functionality.</li>
            <li>Send demo appointment confirmations and reminders (simulated).</li>
            <li>Provide support for project testing and feedback.</li>
            <li>Analyze and improve the app for educational purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>Since this is a demo app:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Data is <strong>not sold or shared with third parties</strong>.</li>
            <li>Data may be used internally by the developer or project team for testing and evaluation.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Login and Account Information</h2>
        <p>- Users log in via Facebook Messenger for demonstration purposes.</p>
        <p>- Messenger login links demo bookings to your Messenger account to show interaction with the bot.</p>
        <p>- No posts will be made to your Facebook account, and no unrelated data is accessed.</p>

        <h2>5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We follow reasonable practices to protect demo data, but no sensitive real-world information should be entered. This app is for educational testing only.</p>

        <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access or delete your demo data by contacting the project team.</li>
            <li>Revoke Messenger permissions at any time through Facebook.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>7. Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p>This app is <strong>not intended for children under 13</strong>. Any data entered by minors is for demonstration only.</p>

        <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>This privacy policy may be updated as the project develops. Updates will be noted with the effective date.</p>

        <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this educational demo, contact:</p>
        <p>
            <strong>Jaylon Dental Clinic Booking (Educational Demo)</strong><br>
            Website: <a href="https://jaylon-dental-clinic-booking-system.onrender.com">Jaylon Dental Clinic</a>
